<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %> 게임</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; }
        .header { background-color: #333; color: white; padding: 10px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
        .container { padding: 20px; }
        .game-frame { width: 100%; height: 600px; border: 1px solid #ddd; margin-top: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h4><%= title %></h4>
        <a href="/portfolio" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-light">포트폴리오로 돌아가기</a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container">
        <h2>게임 플레이</h2>
        <p>아래에서 게임을 플레이하거나 새 창에서 열 수 있습니다.</p>
        
        <div class="d-flex mb-3">
            <button class="btn btn-primary me-2" onclick="openNewWindow()">새 창에서 열기</button>
            <button class="btn btn-success" onclick="embedGame()">게임 표시하기</button>
        </div>
        
        <div id="gameContainer"></div>
    </div>
    
    <script>
        function openNewWindow() {
            window.open('https://app.codingnplay.co.kr/game-proxy/vnc.html?path=/game-proxy/websockify&autoconnect=true', '<%= title %>', 'width=1024,height=768');
        }
        
        function embedGame() {
            document.getElementById('gameContainer').innerHTML = 
                '<iframe src="https://app.codingnplay.co.kr/game-proxy/vnc.html?path=/game-proxy/websockify&autoconnect=true" class="game-frame"></iframe>';
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>